<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5912&amp;p=54834#p54834"><![CDATA[
Most emus do everything in software, pixel at a time.<br /><br />The NES does too many timing sensitive raster tricks to effectively take advantage of hardware acceleration.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=33">Disch</a> — Thu Jan 07, 2010 9:14 pm</p><hr />
